<m0>Nen, Marlins make it 2 straight<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   LINE 1 IS 1.05 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m4>   TOTAL HEAD DEPTH IS .618 INCHES<m2><ql>
